6	1	05_security-passes-for-07-jul-2026-meeting_digital.pdf	b6b3232af7995bd18f7784d0eb5055dc420f5415fc9a1ae13c8730bb472528dc	/home/coder/project/backend/uploads/docs/u1_05_security-passes-for-07-jul-2026-meeting_digital.pdf	pdf	1	E-mail: dacids-ict.ids@nic.in\n\n## HQ Integrated Defence Staff\n\nOps Branch (Dte of ICT&amp;N) Room No 006, 'B' Block, Ground Floor Defence Offices Complex, Africa Avenue New Delhi-110023\n\nIDS/Ops/ICT&amp;N/33018/AI/05\n\n## As per distr list\n\n## Subject: SECURITY PASSES FOR 07 JUL 2026 MEETING : FORWARDING OF AADHAAR DETAILS\n\n1. The first working-level meeting of the Empowered Committee is scheduled for 1430 hrs on 07 Jul 2026 at Defence Offices Complex, Africa Avenue.\n2. Aadhaar details of civilian personnel attending are requested to be forwarded by 06 Jul 2026 to enable timely issue of security passes. Entry will not be permitted without a valid pass.\n3. Aadhar Details (For Civilians only) : The Aadhar details of the personnel attending may kindly be fwd on mail dacids-ict.ids@nic.in for security pass purposes.\n\nConfirmation / reply-by date: 06 Jul 2026.\n\ndt 05 Jul 26\n\n(R K Menon) Gp Capt Jt Dir ICT&amp;N (for ACIDS)	event	done	\N	2026-07-08 06:59:47.529228	IDS/Ops/ICT&N/33018/AI/05	replied
7	1	06_nomination-of-members-for-empowered-comm_scan.pdf	020294d1df03d878ffa1c9acdef71db42a86586235d6b9c47c1a127acd241c64	/home/coder/project/backend/uploads/docs/u1_06_nomination-of-members-for-empowered-comm_scan.pdf	pdf	1	Tele\n\n20867588\n\nFax\n\n20861921\n\nE-mail: dacids-ict.ids@nicin\n\n## HQ Integrated Defence Staff\n\nOps Branch (Dte of ICTSN) Room No 006, 'B' Block, Ground Floor Defence Offices Complex, Africa Avenue New Delhi-110023\n\nIDSIOpsIICTSN/33018/A//06\n\nAs per distr list\n\n## Subject: NOMINATION OF MEMBERS FOR EMPOWERED COMMITTEE REMINDER\n\n- 2 Nominations few Directorates are still awaited. receipt is delaying finalisation of the ahead of the first working-level meeting. committee composition from Non-\n1. Reference this HQ letter IDS/OpsIICTSN/33018/Al/02 dt 26 Jun 2026 on the subject\n- 3 It is once again requested that nominations be forwarded to this HQ by 05 Jul 2026 without fail Confirmation / reply-by date: 05 Jul 2026.\n\ndt 03 Jul 26\n\n(R K Menon) Gp Capt Jt Dir ICTSN (for ACIDS)	task	done	\N	2026-07-08 06:59:51.134748	IDS/OpsIICTSN/33018/A//06	open
3	1	02_constitution-of-empowered-committee-on-a_digital.pdf	fd1b3fd11d379c90e520ef769885df97fde07953ce054fa7433637374e50738b	/home/coder/project/backend/uploads/docs/u1_02_constitution-of-empowered-committee-on-a_digital.pdf	pdf	1	E-mail: dacids-ict.ids@nic.in\n\n## HQ Integrated Defence Staff\n\nOps Branch (Dte of ICT&amp;N) Room No 006, 'B' Block, Ground Floor Defence Offices Complex, Africa Avenue New Delhi-110023\n\nIDS/Ops/ICT&amp;N/33018/AI/02\n\n## As per distr list\n\n## Subject: CONSTITUTION OF EMPOWERED COMMITTEE ON AI BASED MULTI SYSTEM DATA FUSION : NOMINATION OF MEMBERS\n\n1. Reference minutes of the coordination meeting held on 22 Jun 2026 vide IDS/Ops/ICT&amp;N/33018/AI/01 dt 24 Jun 2026.\n2. In order to constitute the Empowered Committee, each Service HQ and concerned Directorate is requested to nominate one officer of the rank of Col/equivalent, preferably with a background in AI, data engineering or C4I systems.\n3. Nominations, along with contact details, are requested to be forwarded to this HQ latest by 02 Jul 2026 to enable finalisation of the committee composition.\n\nAadhar Details (For Civilians only) : The Aadhar details of the personnel attending may kindly be fwd on mail dacids-ict.ids@nic.in for security pass purposes.\n\nConfirmation / reply-by date: 02 Jul 2026.\n\n## Distribution:\n\nArmy HQ (DGIS) Air HQ (ACAS Ops) Naval HQ (ACNS) HQ IDS (Ops/Int/ICT&amp;N) M/s Indihood (for presentation)\n\ndt 26 Jun 26\n\n(DS Joshi) AVM ACIDS (ICT)	task	done	\N	2026-07-08 06:59:36.917787	IDS/Ops/ICT&N/33018/AI/02	open
2	1	01_minutes-of-coordination-meeting-on-ai-ba_digital.pdf	727c3124063bfd8f0a3a7061acd33a70586276a175c21044006fd181b4d313ac	/home/coder/project/backend/uploads/docs/u1_01_minutes-of-coordination-meeting-on-ai-ba_digital.pdf	pdf	1	## HQ Integrated Defence Staff\n\nOps Branch (Dte of ICT&amp;N) Room No 006, 'B' Block, Ground Floor Defence Offices Complex, Africa Avenue New Delhi-110023\n\nIDS/Ops/ICT&amp;N/33018/AI/01\n\n## As per distr list\n\n## Subject: MINUTES OF COORDINATION MEETING ON AI BASED MULTI SYSTEM DATA FUSION HELD ON 22 JUN 2026\n\n1. A coordination meeting was held at CDS Conference Hall on 22 Jun 2026 under the directions of CISC to review indigenous capability for AI based multi system data fusion across the three Services.\n2. A presentation on 'Indigenous Deterministic Software Coding Capability and its Application to Tri Services AI based Multi System Data Fusion and Decision Support Tool' was given by M/s Indihood. Following deliberations, a decision was taken to constitute an Empowered Committee (EC) with experts from diverse fields.\n3. All Directorates are requested to nominate one officer of the rank of Col/equivalent as member. Nominations may reach this HQ by 02 Jul 2026.\n\nNominations reply-by: 02 Jul 2026.\n\ndt 24 Jun 26\n\n(R K Menon) Gp Capt Jt Dir ICT&amp;N (for ACIDS)	task	done	\N	2026-07-08 06:59:33.47224	IDS/Ops/ICT&N/33018/AI/01	open
