4	1	03_empowered-committee-on-ai-based-multi-sy_scan.pdf	64a6bc2dd2e35d6ea091cd08debe63c703bbd7df99cbbc68dff4267fe8e39693	/home/coder/project/backend/uploads/docs/u1_03_empowered-committee-on-ai-based-multi-sy_scan.pdf	pdf	1	Tele\n\n20867588\n\nFax\n\n20861921\n\nE-mail: dacids-ict ids@nic.in\n\n## HQ Integrated Defence Staff\n\nOps Branch (Dte of ICTSN) Room No 006, B' Block, Ground Floor Defence Offices Complex, Africa Avenue New Delhi-110023\n\nIDSIOpsIICTSN/33018/A//03\n\nAs per distr list\n\n## Subject: EMPOWERED COMMITTEE ON Al BASED MULTI SYSTEM DATA FUSION : MEETING\n\n- 1.\n2. A presentation on development of 'Indigenous Deterministic Software Coding Capability and its Application to Tri Services Al based Multi System Data Fusion and Decision Support Tool' for multiple levels of Command across Services was given by Mls Indihood, following which a decision was taken to form an Empowered Committee (EC) on the subject with experts from diverse fields.\n- 3 In order to firm up the Terms of Reference for the Committee; a first working level meeting will be held in New Delhi as under: -\n\nDate &amp; Time\n\n1430 hrs on 07 Jul 2026\n\nVenue\n\nICT Division Conference Hall, Room No 015, 'B' Block, Ground Floor, Defence Offices Complex, Africa Avenue, New Delhi-110023\n\nAadhar Details (For Civilians only) The Aadhar details of the personnel attending may kindly be fwd on mail dacids-ict ids@nic.in for security pass purposes.\n\n4. The Committee will have to submit its report within six weeks of its convening and bring out the operational accruements to the defence forces coming out of this proposed solution.\n2. 5 Member Secretary for the committee will be the undersigned.\n\nDistribution: Army HQ (DGIS) Air HQ (ACAS Ops) Naval HQ (ACNS) Mls Indihood (for presentation)\n\ndt 06 Jul 26\n\n(DS Joshi) AVM ACIDS (ICT)	event	done	\N	2026-07-08 06:59:40.62662	IDSIOpsIICTSN/33018/A//03	open
